English: Required for Magento App inside Zendesk to work.
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 供 Zendesk 内部的 Magento App 运作所需。

English: Successfully generated a new API token
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 已成功生成新的 API 密钥

English: Create tickets from Contact Us form
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 从“联系我们”窗体创建工单

English: Decide which features you would like turned on in your Magento store.
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 决定您希望在 Magento 商店中打开的功能。

English: Used to link order in Magento with tickets in Zendesk
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 用于链接 Magento 订单与 Zendesk 工单

English: Show support tickets on customer view
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 在客户视图中显示支持工单

English: Show support tickets on admin dashboard
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 在管理员面板中显示支持工单

English: Show support tickets on order view
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 在订单视图中显示支持工单

English: General settings that are required to connect Zendesk and Magento.
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 用于连接 Zendesk 和 Magento 的通用设置。

English: To generate a token, log in to Zendesk then select Manage > Channels > API > Token
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 要生成密钥，登录 Zendesk 然后选择管理 > 渠道 > API > 密钥

English: Haven't setup Zendesk yet? Follow our easy setup guide to start using Zendesk to support your customers.
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 尚未设置 Zendesk？跟着我们的简易设置指南，开始使用 Zendesk 支持客户。

English: Use Magento to manage user authentication.
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 使用 Magento 管理用户身份验证。

English: Zendesk allows your customers to contact you using the methods they prefer. Use the links below to configure the channels you would like to use.
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): Zendesk 允许您的客户用其偏好的方式联系您。使用下面的链接配置您希望使用的渠道。

English: Zendesk domain not set. Please add this to the settings page.
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): Zendesk 域名尚未设置。请将此添加至设置页面。

English: No views selected. Please select one or more from the settings page.
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): 未选择视图。请从设置页面选择一个或多个。

English: Zendesk SSO token not been set. Please add this to the settings page.
简体中文 (Simplified Chinese): Zendesk SSO 密钥尚未设置。请将此添加至设置页面。
在 Zendesk 中查看工单
